01:05:45,441 --> 01:05:46,442
Chief.

765
01:05:53,407 --> 01:05:54,617
Yes, this is he.

766
01:05:58,454 --> 01:06:01,540
Yes, thank you. Sure.

767
01:06:05,294 --> 01:06:08,172
It was Captain Jang at
the Women & Juvenile Affairs Division.

768
01:06:08,297 --> 01:06:09,674
He said we did good work.

769
01:06:09,799 --> 01:06:12,468
<i>Last week, the public was outraged
to hear a corrupt detective</i>

770
01:06:12,551 --> 01:06:15,388
<i>only receiving a fine
on illegal prostitution charges</i>

771
01:06:15,471 --> 01:06:17,223
<i>due to insufficient evidence.</i>

772
01:06:17,306 --> 01:06:21,519
<i>Today, yet another case
has caught the public's attention.</i>

773
01:06:22,061 --> 01:06:25,690
<i>Three months ago,
a high-ranking officer, while intoxicated,</i>

774
01:06:25,773 --> 01:06:30,194
<i>gravely injured a restaurant waiter
with his firearm for trying to stop him.</i>

775
01:06:30,277 --> 01:06:32,571
<i>Though he was dismissed,
the public is still--</i>

776
01:06:32,655 --> 01:06:34,615
Don't pay it any attention.

777
01:06:34,699 --> 01:06:37,201
Those bastards only want to bring us down.

778
01:06:37,284 --> 01:06:38,703
<i>It is still being investigated.</i>

779
01:06:38,786 --> 01:06:39,996
Did you meet the doctor?

780
01:06:40,079 --> 01:06:43,207
<i>It has been confirmed that
he has been sent to the Police Agency.</i>

781
01:06:43,290 --> 01:06:46,252
He came out during surgery to brief us.

782
01:06:47,586 --> 01:06:48,838
What did he say?

783
01:06:52,383 --> 01:06:53,551
What is it?

784
01:06:55,011 --> 01:06:56,303
Well...

785
01:06:57,388 --> 01:06:58,431
First,

786
01:06:59,557 --> 01:07:03,227
surgery was successful
on his spleen and kidney.

787
01:07:04,562 --> 01:07:05,604
But?

788
01:07:10,234 --> 01:07:12,236
He still has to gain consciousness,

789
01:07:13,237 --> 01:07:14,488
so we'll have to see.

790
01:07:16,574 --> 01:07:17,575
Also,

791
01:07:19,285 --> 01:07:21,537
the assailant cut

792
01:07:22,496 --> 01:07:25,583
Yang-chon's ligament behind his right knee
with the knife.

793
01:07:28,169 --> 01:07:29,712
The doctor will do his best but...

794
01:07:35,551 --> 01:07:36,761
Are you saying he might not

795
01:07:38,721 --> 01:07:40,306
be able to run anymore?

796
01:08:03,329 --> 01:08:04,413
Sang-su.

797
01:08:05,790 --> 01:08:07,374
Don't wash your uniform.

798
01:08:08,501 --> 01:08:09,668
Sang-su.

799
01:08:10,252 --> 01:08:11,837
Open this door!

800
01:08:12,421 --> 01:08:13,422
Sang-su!

801
01:08:14,298 --> 01:08:15,758
Open this door.

802
01:08:16,801 --> 01:08:18,511
Sang-su!

803
01:08:18,594 --> 01:08:19,804
Open up.

804
01:08:21,514 --> 01:08:23,808
Do you think I can't open it myself?

805
01:08:41,325 --> 01:08:42,326
Mom.

806
01:08:44,078 --> 01:08:46,372
I don't care
if you weren't the one who was stabbed.

807
01:08:46,622 --> 01:08:48,374
You'll quit immediately.

808
01:08:48,749 --> 01:08:51,877
We don't need this job to get by.

809
01:08:52,753 --> 01:08:54,839
There are other jobs you can get.

810
01:08:55,047 --> 01:08:56,340
Mom.

811
01:08:57,383 --> 01:08:58,717
This doesn't happen all the time.

812
01:08:59,969 --> 01:09:00,845
Also,

813
01:09:03,055 --> 01:09:04,390
I caught the assailant.

814
01:09:04,723 --> 01:09:07,393
Who cares if you did?

815
01:09:07,476 --> 01:09:10,563
Your mentor, who's brighter
and more skilled, got injured.

816
01:09:10,938 --> 01:09:13,149
It could happen to you too!

817
01:09:13,232 --> 01:09:16,235
Catching one bad guy
won't stop others from committing crimes.

818
01:09:16,986 --> 01:09:18,320
As of today,

819
01:09:18,863 --> 01:09:20,156
you're quitting this job.

820
01:09:22,867 --> 01:09:24,535
Every day when you head to work,

821
01:09:24,743 --> 01:09:26,537
my heart shrivels out of worry.

822
01:09:27,538 --> 01:09:30,499
You'll stay home from this day on.

823
01:09:33,586 --> 01:09:35,337
I'm putting my foot down.

824
01:09:35,588 --> 01:09:38,048
Quit your job as a cop.

825
01:10:38,442 --> 01:10:39,735
I'm going to bed early.

826
01:10:42,863 --> 01:10:44,490
I'm here to join you.

827
01:10:54,917 --> 01:10:55,918
Lie down.

828
01:11:21,819 --> 01:11:22,987
Lieutenant Oh's surgery

829
01:11:24,989 --> 01:11:26,240
went well.

830
01:11:26,824 --> 01:11:28,659
I saw it in our chat room.

831
01:11:32,788 --> 01:11:34,081
Is he conscious?

832
01:11:36,500 --> 01:11:37,418
Close your eyes.

833
01:13:28,320 --> 01:13:30,155
SEOUL MAHYEON POLICE STATION

834
01:13:33,450 --> 01:13:36,161
INVESTIGATION ROOM

835
01:13:36,245 --> 01:13:38,705
The internal investigation
is just a formality.

836
01:13:38,789 --> 01:13:39,998
Judging from the situation,

837
01:13:40,082 --> 01:13:42,292
we're convinced
that he's the prime suspect,

838
01:13:42,876 --> 01:13:44,878
so you don't need to worry too much.

839
01:13:45,921 --> 01:13:46,922
Okay.

840
01:13:47,714 --> 01:13:48,715
Thank you.

841
01:13:57,641 --> 01:13:59,309
Hey, we have a problem.

842
01:14:00,269 --> 01:14:02,271
Yeom Sang-su shot the wrong guy.

843
01:14:02,563 --> 01:14:04,022
Chief wants to meet. Let's go.

844
01:14:04,231 --> 01:14:05,232
<i>Breaking news.</i>

845
01:14:05,315 --> 01:14:09,528
<i>Early this morning, the prime suspect
in the recent serial murders</i>

846
01:14:09,611 --> 01:14:13,157
<i>that have been occurring
in Jangnam, Jangdong, and Mahyeon areas</i>

847
01:14:13,740 --> 01:14:15,701
<i>was caught by brave civilians.</i>

848
01:14:16,743 --> 01:14:20,205
<i>TN News exclusively obtained this footage</i>

849
01:14:20,289 --> 01:14:24,168
<i>from a security camera
near Seohyeon Park at Dongdaemun.</i>

850
01:14:24,251 --> 01:14:26,336
<i>Around 5:42 a.m., a janitor</i>

851
01:14:26,420 --> 01:14:28,338
<i>saw an elderly woman, who was exercising,</i>

852
01:14:28,422 --> 01:14:31,800
<i>getting attacked and dragged
to a public washroom by the suspect</i>

853
01:14:31,884 --> 01:14:33,802
<i>You're watching the janitor
screaming for help</i>

854
01:14:33,886 --> 01:14:37,014
<i>and the passersby catching
the suspect together.</i>

855
01:14:37,806 --> 01:14:40,350
<i>What's utterly shocking is that
the police thought</i>

856
01:14:40,434 --> 01:14:43,270
<i>that they had the serial killer in custody</i>

857
01:14:43,353 --> 01:14:44,897
<i>and had completely let their guard down.</i>

858
01:14:45,647 --> 01:14:47,900
<i>According to an insider
at Mahyeon Police Station,</i>

859
01:14:47,983 --> 01:14:51,904
<i>the gloves used
in the Mahyeon Park Incident two days ago</i>

860
01:14:51,987 --> 01:14:55,115
<i>were cotton, not leather.</i>

861
01:14:55,199 --> 01:14:57,951
<i>And unlike the serial killer,
the suspect used a scalpel,</i>

862
01:14:58,035 --> 01:15:00,412
-Mom, Dad is conscious.
<i>-so the police knew that it's likely</i>

863
01:15:00,496 --> 01:15:02,206
-Okay.
<i>-to be just a copycat crime,</i>

864
01:15:02,289 --> 01:15:04,666
<i>but the higher-ups overlooked
the possibility.</i>

865
01:15:04,750 --> 01:15:06,835
<i>Kang, the man suspected to be the killer,</i>

866
01:15:06,919 --> 01:15:09,171
<i>is a medical student
with a proven academic track record.</i>

867
01:15:09,254 --> 01:15:11,924
<i>He also has firm alibis
to prove his whereabouts</i>

868
01:15:12,007 --> 01:15:16,386
<i>on the days
of the first, second, and third murders.</i>

869
01:15:16,762 --> 01:15:18,764
<i>Around 2 p.m. today, a body cam footage</i>

870
01:15:18,847 --> 01:15:21,892
<i>from the day of the incident
was posted on social media.</i>

871
01:15:21,975 --> 01:15:24,144
<i>After watching the footage, Kang's family</i>

872
01:15:24,228 --> 01:15:26,688
<i>filed a complaint against Officer Yeom,</i>

873
01:15:26,772 --> 01:15:31,151
<i>who shot Kang for professional negligence.</i>

874
01:15:31,235 --> 01:15:34,029
<i>Here's the body cam footage.</i>

875
01:15:34,363 --> 01:15:35,322
<i>Don't move!</i>

876
01:15:35,405 --> 01:15:36,823
BREAKING NEWS, BODY CAM FOOTAGE

877
01:15:36,907 --> 01:15:37,908
<i>Drop the knife.</i>

878
01:15:39,618 --> 01:15:40,619
<i>Don't kill me.</i>

879
01:15:41,828 --> 01:15:42,829
<i>I dropped the knife.</i>

880
01:16:16,488 --> 01:16:18,240
Forget the manual.
Anyone in that situation--

881
01:16:18,323 --> 01:16:20,617
Anyone would've shot the guy.
I know I would've.

882
01:16:21,201 --> 01:16:22,953
<i>You're saying that anyone would've</i>

883
01:16:23,036 --> 01:16:25,956
shot the guy in that situation,
but I can't agree with that, Jeong-o.

884
01:16:26,039 --> 01:16:28,709
The victim is
a complete stranger to us, but...

885
01:16:28,792 --> 01:16:32,212
<i>What Sang-su did
isn't what anyone would've done.</i>

886
01:16:33,046 --> 01:16:34,631
<i>Why didn't he follow the manual</i>

887
01:16:34,715 --> 01:16:36,216
<i>and cause this mess?</i>

888
01:16:36,925 --> 01:16:37,968
No.

889
01:16:40,137 --> 01:16:41,346
Mr. Oh Yang-chon.

890
01:16:42,139 --> 01:16:44,266
Subtitle translation by Hye-lim Park
